name: Alora Naturals Cayenne 40,000 SHU 500mg - 90 Vegetarian Capsules
description:
Cayenne 40,000 SHU or Capsicum assists in regulating blood flow and is helpful to the cardiovascular system by strengthening the heart, arteries, capillaries, nerves and reducing blood cholesterol and triglyceride levels . Cayenne is also suitable for those with insufficient peripheral circulation with cold hands, and feet, chilblains. When taken with meals, cayenne aids in digestion.

Traditionally, cayenne was used to sooth the digestive tract as it would stimulate the flow of saliva and stomach secretions. These secretions contain substances that help digest food. Cayenne is also used to relieve constipation, gas and bloating, as it stimulates gastric secretions. Cayenne can be an effective remedy for relieving congestion and coughs. It acts to thin mucus, improving the flow of body fluids. Cayenne has also been used externally to relieve rheumatic pain.

name: Waist Away Green Coffee Bean - 90 Capsules
description: Green coffee bean extract has become a big player in the weight-loss game, thanks to a glowing recommendation from a popular TV doctor. Its biggest claim to fame is its ability to help slow the release of sugar into the bloodstream, which means less fat storage, especially in the abdominal area. The gradual release also helps to prevent energy dips that often cue carb cravings for a quick power up.

name: Waist Away Garcinia Cambogia - 90 Capsules
description:
Garcinia Cambogia, also known as garcinia gummi-gutta, gambooge and a few other interesting names, is a tropical fruit from Indonesia. It ranges in colour from green to a pale yellow, and looks a lot like a miniature pumpkin. Thanks to its Hydroxycitric Acid (HCA), our tropical fruit friend has become a big-time supporter in fat loss.

HCA has been praised for its ability to stop fat formation by inhibiting an enzyme, citrate lypase, which is responsible for converting unused blood sugar into pounds. It also helps to reduce your appetite by having a positive impact on serotonin. This neurotransmitter is responsible for making you feel good, so you dont have those unwanted sugar cravings or weakened willpower.

name: Alora Naturals Green Coffee Bean 400mg - 60 Vegetarian Capsules
description: Alora Naturals Green Coffee Bean is an all natural weight loss agent that is a powerful insulin stabilizer and antioxidant.  The green (raw) coffee bean contains high amounts of chlorogenic acid, which inhibits an enzyme, glucose-6-phosphate, that promotes the formation of glucose in the liver.  By slowing down the absorption of glucose in the bloodstream, the chlorogenic acid thus reduces the absorption of fat.
